.IX Subsection "trim"
.Vb 1
\&  $validation = $validation\->optional(\*(Aqfoo\*(Aq, \*(Aqtrim\*(Aq);
.Ve
.PP
Trim whitespace characters from both ends of string value with
\&\*(L"trim\*(R" in Mojo::Util.
